text: Nicole Macri is an American politician, who was elected to the Washington House of Representatives in the 2016 elections."No progress on education funding as 2017 Washington Legislature opens, but Inslee hopeful". KCPQ, January 9, 2017. A member of the Democratic Party, she represents the 43rd district. Prior to her election to the legislature, Macri served as deputy director of Seattle's Downtown Emergency Service Center."The Stranger Endorses Nicole Macri for 43rd State Representative!".
